{
  "stem": "4753.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because during the time, as the school got smaller and smaller, the children wrote to the organization, if I let go, they want to leave, too.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was teaching two and a half years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And children from age 10, that was just a few, till 20.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had one pupil who was 20 years old, older than me, and she couldn't write, so I taught her how to write.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said that was her happiest moment in her life, when she could write a letter to her brother, whom she found out, during that time, you know, that they are alive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after the school wounded up, because the children were transported to Israel-- they did go, many of them, [INAUDIBLE], and to America, and wherever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some returned to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got, as a schol-- as a reward from the Jewish organization, a scholarship to do whatever I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wanted to study to be a bacteriologist technologist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's what I became in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I did go, in Sweden, to college.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, in the same time, I did work in a hospital right away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What possessed you to do that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To study bacteriology?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to be, originally, a teacher, because I wanted to teach the world to like each other, when the Nazis started and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was very interested in the medical field.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe that triggered-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just wanted to help people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I am still, today, very interested in everything new.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And especially now, for my husband, I, I wrote and called, plastic and other kind of factories and doctors, and UCLA, and everywhere.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where I did go, I did work at UCLA.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked at USC.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
